snippet: The battle over whether to allow employers to opt out of contraception coverage may be over in the Senate, but House Speaker John A. Boehner signaled Thursday that House Republicans will continue the fight.
abstract: The battle over whether to allow employers to opt out of contraception coverage may be over in the Senate, but House Speaker John A. Boehner signaled Thursday that House Republicans will continue the fight.

headline.main: Boehner Vows to Continue Contraception Fight
